[ext_resource type="Script" path="res://scripts/main_menu.gd" id="1_mm"]

; Landing screen: loaded at boot, no 3D world attached. Picks which
; scene to actually run (main.tscn for the game, blueprint_editor.tscn
; for authoring). Cursor is free; no physics ticking; low cost.

